JOHN ROBERTSON of Pr. Geo.
Co., 330 acs. NL in sd Co. on S
side Buckskin Cr., at Walls Path;
adj. his father, Henry Baby,
Morgan McKinny & David Walker;
3 Dec 1733, p.135. £1.S15.

WILLIAM IVY, Gent., 36 acs. NL
in Norf. Co., N side Tanners Cr.;
6 April 1734, p.200. 5 Shill.

JOSEPH MORETON (Morton) of
Pr. Geo. Co., 225 acs. NL in sd
Co., S side of Appamattox Riv.;
bet. sd Moreton, Pride, & Mayo;
25 May 1734, p.224. £1.85.

JOHN MASON, 335 acs. Surry
Co., S side of the main black
Water Sw., S side of Reedy Br.;
adj. Richard Bland & John Ellison;
24 Mar 1734/35, p.472. £1.S15.
